<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="catalog_script_client"><catalog_script_client action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><applies_catalog>true</applies_catalog><applies_extended>false</applies_extended><applies_req_item>false</applies_req_item><applies_sc_task>false</applies_sc_task><applies_target_record>false</applies_target_record><applies_to>item</applies_to><cat_item display_value="F5 Build Virtual Server">e03fc46347448e10927bb5f4316d4319</cat_item><cat_variable>IO:e43df590471c8250927bb5f4316d43cb</cat_variable><condition/><description/><field/><global>true</global><isolate_script>false</isolate_script><messages/><name>F5AS3ClientScript01</name><order/><script><![CDATA[function onChange(control, oldValue, newValue, isLoading) {
    if (isLoading || newValue === '') {
        return;
    }

    var env = g_form.getValue("env");
    var update_as3_tenant = g_form.getValue("update_as3_tenant");
    var vs_name = g_form.getValue("vs_name");

    //call script
    var ga = new GlideAjax('F5GetAS3VIP');
    ga.addParam('sysparm_name', 'getAS3Info');
    ga.addParam('sysparm_env', env);
    ga.addParam('sysparm_vs_name', vs_name);
    ga.addParam('sysparm_update_as3_tenant', update_as3_tenant);
    ga.getXMLAnswer(getResponse);


    function getResponse(response) {
        console.log("response is =" + response);
        var jsonObj = JSON.parse(response);

        var tenant = jsonObj[update_as3_tenant];

        var vs = vs_name + "_vs";
        var cert = vs_name + "_cert";
        var pool = vs_name + "_pool";

        g_form.setValue("vip_address", tenant[vs_name][vs].virtualAddresses);
        g_form.setValue("vs_port", tenant[vs_name][vs].virtualPort);
        g_form.setValue("import_cert", tenant[vs_name][cert].certificate);
        g_form.setValue("import_key", tenant[vs_name][cert].privateKey);

        var port = tenant[vs_name][pool].members[0].servicePort;
        var poolArr = tenant[vs_name][pool].members[0].serverAddresses;
        var mvrsPoolArr = [];
        for (var i = 0; i < poolArr.length; i++) {
            var poolObj = {};
            poolObj.server_name = "";
            poolObj.server_ip = poolArr[i];
            poolObj.server_port = port;
            mvrsPoolArr.push(poolObj);
        }

        g_form.setValue("pool_members", JSON.stringify(mvrsPoolArr));

    }
}]]></script><sys_class_name>catalog_script_client</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2024-02-05 15:26:44</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>8c8fbaaf4740ce10927bb5f4316d43dd</sys_id><sys_mod_count>56</sys_mod_count><sys_name>F5AS3ClientScript01</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>catalog_script_client_8c8fbaaf4740ce10927bb5f4316d43dd</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2024-02-07 19:02:41</sys_updated_on><table/><type>onChange</type><ui_type>10</ui_type><variable_set/><view/></catalog_script_client></record_update>
